item.title: Meetup - Tuesday 5th June 2018 at Platform in Leeds
item.description: With just over 200 shopping days until Christmas it must be time for the June devops meetup at Platform in Leeds on Tuesday 5th June 2018. Yet again we have a bumper line up for you: 6:45 - 7:15 : Doors open, have a chat, make some new devops friends 7:15 - 7:25 : Group updates/news/announcements - Findmypast 7:25 - 8:05 : True North Operations 8:05 - 8:20 : Intermission
